><button class=\"language-button\" aria-label=\"Switch language to मराठी\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.language.toggle\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-languages\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m5 8 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m4 14 6-6 2-3\"></path><path d=\"M2 5h12\"></path><path d=\"M7 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m22 22-5-10-5 10\"></path><path d=\"M14 18h6\"></path></svg><span>मराठी</span></button><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.cta.contact\" class=\"button button-primary button-sm desktop-cta\" href=\"/contact\">Let’s talk<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">↗</span></a><button class=\"menu-button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Open navigation\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.mobile-menu.open\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 18h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 6h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"page-hero\"><div class=\"page-hero-orb\"></div><div class=\"container\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">Learn before you decide</span><h1>Financial literacy for real life.</h1><p>Clear language, relatable examples and practical systems—so financial knowledge becomes a habit, not just information.</p></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container learning-grid\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">Our learning philosophy</span><h2>Understanding grows when the jargon leaves the room.</h2><p class=\"large-copy\">We teach the why behind financial habits—cash flow, protection, goals, risk and discipline—without hype or fear.</p></div><div class=\"learning-steps\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><span>0<!-- -->1</span><strong>Start with your everyday reality</strong></div><div><span>0<!-- -->2</span><strong>Make concepts visible and understandable</strong></div><div><span>0<!-- -->3</span><strong>Make learning part of repeatable habits</strong></div><div><span>0<!-- -->4</span><strong>Review decisions with greater awareness</strong></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section faq-section\"><div class=\"container faq-grid\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">Frequently asked</span><h2>Good questions are part of the process.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div data-orientation=\"vertical\"><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"accordion-item\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_1llfiujb_\" class=\"accordion-trigger\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"literacy.faq.toggle.1\" data-radix-collection-item=\"\">Is financial literacy the same as investment advice?<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_9llfiujb_\" hidden=\"\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"radix-_R_1llfiujb_\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"accordion-content\" style=\"--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)\"></div></div><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" class=\"accordion-item\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertica